      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 45 六二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 45 六二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六二：引吉，无咎，孚乃利用禴。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second SIX, divided, shows its subject led forward (by his correlate). There will be good fortune, and freedom from error. There is entire sincerity, and in that case (even the small offerings of) the vernal sacrifice are acceptable.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
