      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 45 九四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九四：大吉，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth NINE, undivided, shows its subject in such a state that, if he be greatly fortunate, he will receive no blame.</seg>
      </tuv>
