      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 45 九五</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 45 九五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九五：萃有位，无咎。匪孚，元永貞，悔亡。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth NINE, undivided, shows the union (of all) under its subject in the place of dignity. There will be no error. If any do not have confidence in him, let him see to it that (his virtue) be great, long-continued, and firmly correct, and all occasion for repentance will disappear.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
